{"article_id":"0x1ORQaP47xViEMa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. military conducted a \" defensive \" airstrike against Taliban forces in Afghanistan ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"less than a week after signing a historic peace deal with the militant group .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"U.S. military spokesman Col. Sonny Leggett said in a tweet","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that the airstrike Wednesday was conducted against four Taliban fighters in Nahr-e Saraj , in the Helmand province ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"who","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"were \" actively attacking \" an Afghan National Defense and Security Force","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"( ANDSF )","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"checkpoint .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"\" This was a defensive strike","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to disrupt the attack , \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he added .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" This was our 1st strike against the Taliban in 11 days . \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Leggett ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"who called on the militant group to uphold their commitments to the peace deal","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"signed on Feb. 29 ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"added","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that Taliban forces had conducted 43 attacks on Afghan troops on Tuesday in the same province .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"\" To be clear","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"we are committed to peace ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"however , we have the responsibility","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to defend our ANDSF partners , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Leggett continued .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"\" Afghans & US have complied ( with )","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"our agreements ;","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"however , Talibs appear intent on squandering this","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"( opportunity )","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and ignoring the will of the people for peace . \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Afghanistan ' s interior ministry said","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"four civilians and 11 troops were killed Wednesday in a wave of attacks","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"attributed to the Taliban across the country in the past 24 hours .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Afghan forces killed at least 17 Taliban members during those clashes .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"The Taliban have not claimed responsibility for any of the attacks so far","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"and have not commented on the U.S. airstrike .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"President Trump said Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he spoke on the phone to a Taliban leader ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"making him the first","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"U.S. president","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"believed to have spoken directly to the militant group","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"responsible for the deaths of thousands of U.S. troops in nearly 19 years of fighting in Afghanistan .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` I spoke to the leader of the Taliban today , ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Trump told reporters on the South Lawn .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"`` We had a very good talk . ''","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"He did n't provide any more details ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"but Taliban spokesman Zabiullah Mujahid confirmed","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Trump spoke with Taliban leader Mullah Abdul Ghani Baradar .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Taliban leaders and U.S. envoy Zalmay Khalilzad signed the historic peace deal in Doha , Qatar .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"It lays out a conditions-based path to the withdrawal of American forces from Afghanistan .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"who witnessed the signing of the agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"told Fox News ' Bret Baier on Monday","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that the Trump administration was able to accomplish something","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"the Obama administration could not .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"`` They never got the Taliban to break with Al Qaeda","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"and they never got a commitment","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that says ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"'If I execute the following conditions based","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"--","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that is if the violence levels come down .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"That is , if the security posture for the United States of America is reduced ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"then and only then will we deliver a commensurate footprint inside your country , ''","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Additional peace negotiations between the warring Afghan sides are supposed to begin on March 10 .","depth":3},{"id":64,"text":"However , Afghanistan ' s leaders have already rejected releasing 5,000 Taliban prisoners","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"ahead of launching the talks","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"- a precondition","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"which","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"the militants say","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"was part of the U.S. agreement .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":139,"left":104,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":82,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":71,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":77,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":2,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":3,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":72,"right":74,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","